<D>__{end of the war, which yet rages on and on.}
<A>__{murmuring from the floor and the balcony, in the front row of which mary and elizabeth keckley sit. mary turns her gaze from the floor to watch latham and schell, a few seats away, scrutinize the floor, whispering, latham taking notes. schell holds the leather prospectus folio in his lap. bilbo sits behind them. they study the other ny democrats charles hanson, nelson merrick, henry lanford, homer benson, giles stuart who comprise a cluster of glum uncomfortable passivity on that side of the aisle.}
<D>__{fernando wood (cont'd) robert latham}
